subtitles.original: 改めて言うことでもないけど
subtitles.english: It's not something I need to say again, but

subtitles.original: 今だからこそ言わせて
subtitles.english: Let me say it now because it's the present

subtitles.original: あの日君が見つけてくれること
subtitles.english: That you would find me on that day

subtitles.original: なんとなく予感してたんだ
subtitles.english: I had a feeling somehow

subtitles.original: 走り出した 君にもっと 力をあげたくて
subtitles.english: I wanted to give more strength to you who started running

subtitles.original: ずっと 前に 心決めたんだ
subtitles.english: I made up my mind a long time ago

subtitles.original: 照らし出して グリーンライツ はるか未来を
subtitles.english: Shine out, Green-Lights, on the far future

subtitles.original: きっと いつか 君を照らすまで
subtitles.english: Until it surely shines on you someday

subtitles.original: 今までも いつまでも 隣にいたいのは
subtitles.english: The reason I want to be by your side now and forever

subtitles.original: 輝いた君の顔を 間近で見たいから
subtitles.english: Is because I want to see your shining face up close

subtitles.original: 言葉時々に無力で なかなか
subtitles.english: Words are sometimes powerless, and

subtitles.original: この世界は変わらないけど
subtitles.english: This world doesn't change easily, but

subtitles.original: もし君が持ってる その魔法で
subtitles.english: If with that magic you possess

subtitles.original: 新しい世界を作れるとしたら
subtitles.english: You could create a new world

subtitles.original: なんてね 言ってみただけ そんなの
subtitles.english: Just kidding, I just said it, such a thing

subtitles.original: 本当できるわけない わけがないでしょう
subtitles.english: There's no way it's really possible, right?

subtitles.original: いいよもっと 信じてよ 何度転んでも
subtitles.english: It's okay, believe more, no matter how many times you fall

subtitles.original: 君は 君の やり方でいいのだ
subtitles.english: You're fine just the way you are

subtitles.original: 照らし出して グリーンライツ 立ち向かう未来を
subtitles.english: Shine out, Green-Lights, on the future you face

subtitles.original: きっと いつか 君を照らすまで
subtitles.english: Until it surely shines on you someday

subtitles.original: 堪えきれない夜に 窓辺で泣いていいよ
subtitles.english: You can cry by the window on nights you can't bear

subtitles.original: また晴れた日に 見せ合う 嬉し涙を
subtitles.english: Let's show each other our happy tears on another sunny day

subtitles.original: 走り出した 君にもっと 力をあげたくて
subtitles.english: I wanted to give more strength to you who started running

subtitles.english: You, who waves from afar when looking back

subtitles.original: この先のどこかで 出会える君も
subtitles.english: And you, who I will meet somewhere ahead
